Wa-la hawla wa-la quwata illa billah al-Ali al-Azim. Tamm. Tamm. Tamm." Around the colophon (in red): "Tamma. Tamma. Tamma. Wa-kana tahbiruhu ala yaday abdihi, wa-asir judihi, wa-arif ihsanihi, al-shakir fadlahu, Sulayman ibn Sayf ibn Sulayman ibn Bashir al-Mighfari (?) [one word torn]. Wa-kana al-faragh min dhalika yawm 10 Rabi al-Awwal, sanat 1123 [18 April 1711]."

note: Colophon of Section 1: "Tamma naskh hadha al-juz duha al-Jumah, wa-thamaniyah wa-ishrin min shahr Dhi al-Qadah, sanat sitt sinin wa-arbain sanah bada alf sanah min Hijrat al-Nabi [23 April 1637], salla Allah alayhi wa-sallam. Naskhahu Khalaf ibn Muhammad ibn Khalaf al-Kindi al-Nazwi thumma al-Nahli, ghafara Allah la-hu wa-li-walidayhi wa-li-jami al-Muslimin wa-al-Muslimat, al-ahya minhum wa-al-amwat. Nasakhahu li-nafsihi. Wa-salla Allah ala Sayyidina Muhammad al-Nabi, wa-alihi wa-sallam. Wa-la hawla wa-la quwata illa billah al-Ali al-Azim al-Azim."

title: Treatise on "Nifas" and "Hayd" according to Islamic law : manuscript.
note: Colophon of Section 2: No colophon. Text ends abruptly, as follows: "... fa-li-tajal tuhraha ashrat ayyam wa-haydaha khamsat ashar yawman, fa-tumsiku min al-khamsat ashar al-yawm al-hayd an al-sawm wa-an al-salah ashrat ayyam, wa-tusalli khamsat ashar yawman wa-tasum. Fa-idha qadat al-sawm ala dhalika wa-aradat al-badal badal al-ashr allati kanat tahsabuha haydan alhaqat maaha badal khamsat ayyam hatta tatimma khamst ashar yawman, fa-takunu dhalika istihadah minha. Wa-amma in itaddat fa-anaha hadha jaalat haydaha khamsat ashar yawman wa-al-tuhr shahran. Qala wa-idha arafat waqt ummiha fa-huwa laha, wa-bi-hi takhudhu fi al-iddah al-salah wa-al-sawm ..."

title: Treatise on "Nifas" and "Hayd" according to Islamic law : manuscript.
note: Colophon of Section 3: No colophon. Text ends abruptly, as follows: "... Qultu kayfa nasnau. Fa-ala ma wasfta, fa-alladhi arafna fi dhalika annaha idha mudda biha al-dam bada ayyam haydiha, wa-kana dhalika al-dam sailan aw qatiran aw faidan muttasilan biha intazarat yawman aw yawmayn, mukhayyarah fi dhalika, taqudu fi intizariha inda al-salah wa-al-sawm. Fa-inn mudda biha al-dam fawqa al-yawm aw al-yawmayn fa-qad qala man qala inna alayha badal ..." Followed by three blank leaves.

And ends with: "Ahabbu ila qalbi min al-khuldi mawtinan // idha hawalu fi al-khuldi dhillata amthali." With the following note (in another hand): "Qad intahat hadhihi al-qasidah al-gharra al-mushtamilah ala al-fasahah wa-al-balaghah wa-insijam al-alfaz maa husn al-siyaghah bi-khatt yad munshiiha wa-nazimiha wa-amir riyadiha bi-badi naghamat hamaimiha akhina al-karim wa-sadiqina al-hamim al-bari al-fadil wa-al-lawdhai al-kamil Kiwan Zadah Ahmad Bik Afandi al-Sharji, harasa Allah dhatahu haythu kana, wa-abqahu bi-khayr wa-ihsan, bi-jah al-Nabi, alayhi al-salah wa-al-salam."

Wa-yatluhhu, in shaa Allah, al-juz al-thani min Kitab al-Diya, fima yajuzu min al-sifat, talif al-Shaykh Abi al-Mundhir Salamah ibn Muslim ibn Ibrahim al-Umani."

Wa-kana al-faragh min naskhihi sabah al-Jumah al-zahra, saat al-Qamar, li-ithnatay ashrata laylatin khalat min shahr Muharram al-haram, sanat sab sinin wa-ishrin wa-miah wa-alf sanah min al-Hijrah al-Nabawiyah [18 January 1715].
